test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7ee12a047440>([-10])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7ee12a047440> = [[1, -10], [1, -10, 1], [-10, 1], [-10, 1, -10], [1, -10], [1, -10, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -100 == -10
 +  where -100 = <built-in function prod>([-2, -5, -10])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
